window.bookSummaryJSON = "An ancient derelict yields some unexpected small surprises, and the crew acquires some unusual new crew members.<br><br>Mee Keralatazaku, the rather troublesome ruler of the planet Kanpripticon, has them take her to a very strange and secretive location. <br><br>When they return, all hell breaks loose as the Kipitz try to kill Mee Keralatazaku and everyone else on Kanpripticon.<br><br>She, who must not be annoyed, is now very, very angry."; 
